  "storyboard_markdown": "# Scene Contract: CH005_SC001\n\n## Production Intent\nEstablish the surreal power dynamic between a physically unstable Alice and a languid Caterpillar. The scene relies on height differentials and scale fluctuations to emphasize Alice's loss of control, using hookah smoke as a rhythmic visual element.\n\n## Required Cast\n- alice: Young girl with rapid physical instability (size/neck elongation).\n- caterpillar: Languid, hookah-smoking insect.\n\n## Required Environments\n- mushroom_clearing: Forest setting featuring a large mushroom structure.\n\n## Continuity Constraints\n- Smoke patterns from hookah must remain consistent between shots.\n- Alice's scale relative to the mushroom stem and cap must reflect her current size state (10 inches to 9 feet).\n\n## Beat List\n- BT001: Alice confronts the Caterpillar regarding her identity.\n- BT002: The Caterpillar smokes and questions Alice's changing size.\n- BT003: Alice attempts to recite poetry to prove herself.\n- BT004: Alice fails the recitation and experiences rising frustration.",
